<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1253078-i-m-listening-to-this-book-on-audible">I&#39;m listening to this book on Audible. There are interesting elements ... how people represent themselves vs what people search. However the examples (so far) are both disturbing (race in America) and/or uninteresting (at least for me). The continuous focus on sexual preferences panders to those seeking titillating items instead of educating on broader topics. It is repetitive. Should I finish listening to it?</a>
