<span id="freeTextContainer4054917770077946446">When sociologist ask people if they waste food, people give the only correct answer. It&apos;s wrong to waste food. <br/><br/>When sociologist survey the contents of the same people&apos;s garbage, they get a more accurate answer.<br/><br/>Just imagine how much more information is available trolling through internet searches.<br/></span>
  <span id="freeText4054917770077946446" style="display:none">When sociologist ask people if they waste food, people give the only correct answer. It's wrong to waste food. <br /><br />When sociologist survey the contents of the same people's garbage, they get a more accurate answer.<br /><br />Just imagine how much more information is available trolling through internet searches.<br /></span>
